metadata.name: Summer Memories EDITION
metadata.description:
"Summer Memories" is a photograph taken this summer 2022 in Spain at the "Rapita".  
Couple walking their dog on the national road at the start of the sunset. This edition of 1000 is offered to you to celebrate the end of summer and thank the amazing NFT community. 
Shot with an Olympus Mju II and Kodak Portra 400 film.

Year: 2022

Artist: Saïd CHAARA

Collection: "Summer Memories" EDITION

Camera: Olympus Mju II

Film: Kodak Portra 400

Edition: 1/1000

License: Primary NFT holder is free to use in advertising, display privately and in groups, including virtual galleries, documentaries and essays by the holder of the NFT, as long as the creator is credited. Copyright remains with the creator.
